Package org.cesecore.profiles

Class ProfileBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.internal.UpgradeableDataHashMap
      • org.cesecore.profiles.ProfileBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IUpgradeableData, Profile
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApprovalProfileBase, ValidatorBase
    public abstract class ProfileBase
extends UpgradeableDataHashMap
implements Profile, Serializable
    Base class for all Profile entity beans. Mainly a holder for an UpgradeableDataHashMap, it's meant to be completely agnostic of any implementation details.
    Version:
    $Id: ProfileBase.java 28140 2018-01-30 12:40:30Z andresjakobs $
